data.description: Embrace the Florida lifestyle in this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom block home that effortlessly combines modern comfort with sunshine-filled spaces. Nestled on a generous lot, this residence invites you to experience the perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living. Step inside to an open and airy living space that effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Perfect for entertaining, the layout is accentuated by the warmth of natural light and the allure of modern design. The heart of the home boasts a fully updated kitchen with modern cabinets and countertops, providing both style and functionality. Rest easy knowing that this home comes with a brand-new roof and a recently updated air conditioning system, offering peace of mind and energy efficiency. Enjoy the beauty of the Sunshine State year-round in your private Florida sunroom. Bathed in natural light, this tranquil space provides the perfect backdrop for morning coffee or evening relaxation. The garage has been partly converted. Continue using it as a small studio or convert it back to a closed in garage. The options are endless. The large yard is your canvas for outdoor living. Whether hosting gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air, the possibilities are endless. Conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers this home offers not just a residence but a lifestyle. Minutes away from I4, and within 30 minutes to beaches and downtown Orlando, this ensures that you are well-connected to the best the area has to offer. Make your dream home a reality. Contact us to schedule a showing and uncover the beauty of this Florida-inspired gem.
